CONFIG_GO_ONLINE_1: Servihelper works offline by default, all the data is stored inside the servihelper folder.
CONFIG_GO_ONLINE_10: Then, lets notify servihelper about this shared folder.
CONFIG_GO_ONLINE_11: Click on the next slider button and an input field to paste the system shared folder path will appear.
CONFIG_GO_ONLINE_12: The route to the shared folder changes from Windows, Mac or Linux. In Windows should be something like: G:\My Space\servihelper (letter can change)
CONFIG_GO_ONLINE_2: Please create a security backup before going online.
CONFIG_GO_ONLINE_3: To work online with more administrators we need to specify another folder where the data will be. It cannot be whatever folder, it must be a folder where data files can be updated by more administrators. Then, a shared folder is required. Some common shared folders are:
CONFIG_GO_ONLINE_4: It's necessary to install the desktop app for one of the aboves providers. You will find the app on their respective markets.
CONFIG_GO_ONLINE_5: You also can look up for the desktop app from google search.
CONFIG_GO_ONLINE_6: When you have installed the app, check that the app its running and you're logged.
CONFIG_GO_ONLINE_7: A new virtual drive will appear on your filesystem (D: E: F: whatever)
CONFIG_GO_ONLINE_8: Now, inside the virtual drive, create a new folder, call it 'servihelper' for example. If you are the first one to sync the files then prepare the link to share this new folder.
CONFIG_GO_ONLINE_9: (When the other admins install the same app, they need to use you link and the folder will appear on their filesystem with all the data)

INFO_HOW_TO_WORK: ¬øHow can several managers work at the same time?
INFO_HOW_TO_WORK_ANSWER: The first creates its assignments, exports the data from the home section and leaves it in a site shared by those responsible, the second imports it and creates its assignments, and so on.
INFO__CONTACT: ¬øHow do I report a bug or an improvement?
INFO__DISTRIBUTION_ANSWER: Yes, although it is recommended that you distribute the download link, as a new version may have come out with some correction.
INFO__HOW_TO_SEND_ASSIGNMENTS_ANSWER: When generating an assignment in the -Assignments- section, an assignment sheet appears in the -Image- column. We click on it and we can preview the assignment. Then below, we can copy it to the clipboard to later paste it in whatsapp web, generate a .png image or generate a pdf.
INFO__WHAT_CAN_BE_DONE_ANSWER: All kinds of assignments can be created. You need to create the assignment types, rooms, and participants in advance.
INFO__WHAT_IS_SERVIHELPER_ANSWER: It is a program that runs on the machine. Your data is managed internally, so it never goes to the internet.

APP_LOCKED_WARNING: The app is being used by another admin but seems that didn't closed as expected
TAKE_CONTROL: This happens when the files are saved and immediatly updated on google drive, sharepoint... but after 15 mins of the last save operation, the 'lock' üîí is not released.
TAKE_CONTROL_2: This means that he lost internet in the process or the selected platform didn't updated the files by whatever reason. Please ask him if there has been some problem.
TAKE_CONTROL_3: In case he has files pending to be updated, he must update the files before you work. Then, after you see the changes, restart {{APP_NAME}}.
TAKE_CONTROL_4: In case he has NO pending files, the work has been updated but the release lock has not been updated on the platform, in that case continue to {{APP_NAME}}.
